---
// Landing page for the Pokédex application
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Pokédex</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body { font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif; background: #0a0a0f; color: #f0f0f5; min-height: 100vh; overflow-x: hidden; }

      body::before, body::after {
        content: ''; position: fixed; border-radius: 50%;
        filter: blur(140px); pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
      }
      body::before {
        width: 700px; height: 700px;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(249,115,22,0.13) 0%, transparent 70%);
        top: -250px; right: -150px;
      }
      body::after {
        width: 600px; height: 600px;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(139,92,246,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
        bottom: -200px; left: -150px;
      }

      nav {
        position: relative; z-index: 10;
        display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
        padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
        background: rgba(10,10,15,0.8); backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      }
      nav a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration: none; margin-left: 2rem; transition: color 0.2s; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; }
      nav a:hover { color: #f97316; }
      .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; color: #f97316; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }

      hero {
        position: relative; z-index: 1;
        display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
        justify-content: center; text-align: center;
        padding: 8rem 2rem 6rem; gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem;
        background: rgba(249,115,22,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(249,115,22,0.2);
        color: #f97316; border-radius: 999px; padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
        font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5.5rem); font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.0; letter-spacing: -0.04em;
        background: linear-gradient(160deg, #fff 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.5) 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
      }
      h1 em {
        font-style: normal;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #fb923c 60%, #fbbf24 100%);
        -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1.2rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
        max-width: 460px; line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin-top: 0.5rem; }

      .btn-primary {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #ea6c00 100%);
        color: white; padding: 0.9rem 2.25rem; border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(249,115,22,0.35);
        transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
        position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      }
      .btn-primary::after {
        content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);
      }
      .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(249,115,22,0.45); }

      .btn-secondary {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); padding: 0.9rem 2.25rem; border-radius: 12px;
        text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px); transition: all 0.15s;
      }
      .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #fff; }

      .features {
        position: relative; z-index: 1;
        display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem 6rem;
      }
      .feat {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
        border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.5rem;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px); transition: border-color 0.2s;
      }
      .feat:hover { border-color: rgba(249,115,22,0.25); }
      .feat-icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
      .feat h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; color: #fff; }
      .feat p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); line-height: 1.6; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <span class="logo">Pokédex</span>
      <div>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/pokedex">Pokédex</a>
        <a href="/ai-generator">AI Generator</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <hero>
      <span class="eyebrow">✦ 1025+ Pokémon</span>
      <h1>Explore the<br/><em>Pokémon</em> World</h1>
      <p>Browse every Pokémon, discover stats, types, and abilities — or generate a brand-new one with AI.</p>
      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="/pokedex" class="btn-primary">Open Pokédex</a>
        <a href="/ai-generator" class="btn-secondary">✦ AI Generator</a>
      </div>
    </hero>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>1025+ Pokémon</h3>
        <p>Every species across all 9 generations, with full stats, types, and sprites.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon">🔍</div>
        <h3>Search & Filter</h3>
        <p>Find any Pokémon instantly by name or filter by all 18 types.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon">✦</div>
        <h3>AI Generator</h3>
        <p>Describe a concept and Claude will design a completely original Pokémon.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat">
        <div class="feat-icon">📊</div>
        <h3>Base Stats</h3>
        <p>View HP, Attack, Defense, Speed and more for every Pokémon.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
